   692тЖТ### Parse
   694тЖТThe engine which parses the contents of your file containing environment
   695тЖТvariables is available to use. It accepts a String or Buffer and will return
      тЖТтАж
   705тЖТ#### Options
   707тЖТ##### debug
   721тЖТ### Populate
   723тЖТThe engine which populates the contents of your .env file to `process.env` is available for use. It accepts a target, a source, and options. This is useful for power users who want to supply their own objects.
   724тЖТ
